      • Kit

        public Kit(java.lang.String id,
           ItemStack[] hotbar,
           ItemStack[] armor,
           ItemStack[] inventory,
           ItemStack offhand)
        Create a "kit," or set of items players spawn with in a game
        Parameters:
        id - Unique ID, preferably a UUID. Must not change between server restarts or plugin versions.
        hotbar - ItemStacks for the player to spawn with in its hotbar.
        armor - ItemStacks for the player to spawn equipped with as armor.
        inventory - ItemStacks for the player to spawn with in its main inventory.
        offhand - ItemStack for the player to spawn with in its offhand.
